How to blur image ?

Syntax : 

			<div>
				<img src="path" class="image">
			</div>
			
			
			.image {
			
				filter: blur(3px) brightness(80%) // filter property has diiferent values, we can specify blur,opacity,brightness to modify the image.
			}
			


